age of the process. Please be advised that this information will be treated in a confidential manner. Personal information collected will be used in accordance with the Municipal Freedom of Information and Protection of Privacy Act for the purpose of candidate selection. Further information concerning the collection of personal information should be directed to the Human Resources Manager, Town of Georgina, 26557 Civic Centre Road, Keswick, ON L4P 3G1 (905) 476-4301 ALL TERMS AND CONDITIONS OF THE CURRENT COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT APPLY We thank all candidates for their interest, however, only those being considered will be contacted. The assessment process may include a practical test and/or interview. Compensation $29.42 to $32.68 per hour Closes: 29 August, 2023 Georgina Public Library Keswick , ON Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
