ned Compensation: $23.85 to $25.37 per hour + Health Spending Account (HSA) To Apply: If you are interested in applying for this position, please contact the HR Manager via email at hr@cochranepubliclibrary.ca *Subject line of email should include Competition # referenced above Closing Date: This posting will close at 5pm on Friday, August 25, 2023. Compensation $23.85 - $25.37 per hour. Closes: 25 August, 2023 Cochrane Public Library Cochrane , AB Policies and Terms of Use · jobboard@bcla.bc.ca / BCLA PO BOX 19008, Rocky Point PO, Port Moody, BC V3H 0J1 window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
